            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Numinib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>in honorem domus divinae <lb n="3"/>Emeriti consistentes Cemenelo <lb n="4"/>scholam veterem de suo <expan><abbr>refecer</abbr><ex>unt</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>et dedicaverunt sub cura <lb n="6"/>Iuli Honorati <expan><abbr>proc</abbr><ex>uratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> ex <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>rimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ilo</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Puncta triangularia. Eingemeißelt. Marmor, weiß. Bearbeiterin: V. Pettirossi</p>
            </div>
